User stories

1. As a student, I want to search for tutors so that I can find help for my subjects.
2. As a student, I want to book a tutoring session so that I can improve my understanding.
3. As a tutor, I want to list the subjects i teach so that students can find me.
4. As a tutor, i want to accept tutoring request so that I can schedule sessions.
5. As an admin, I want to manage user accounts so that platform remains safe.
